{When NORTH makes a Splinter bid, showing \H support and \C shortness, 
SOUTH naturally thinks about slam.

She uses RKCB 4NT, and NORTH, with one Key Card and a \C Void, bids 6\C.

Just what SOUTH needed for the 6\H bid.}

